Kunal Joseph

 attended 

 posted on 11 Aug, 2016

					""Well, I thank UrbanPro for setting up a platform by which I met Mr. Vishal J Bhavsar. I am from a non technical background and I was happy that Vishal Sir understood my requirement in our first meeting. He designed the learning in a methodology in which I could relate i.e starting with scratch from learning sketching, engineering drawing, the basics and than he started to teach autocad both 2D and 3D. The course structure was nicely designed and he gave a lot of inputs and time with each chapter. Well I would like to thank Vishal Sir for his time and energy he puts in every student. His skills and knowledge about the subject is exceptional. He communicates well in all 3 prominent languages i.e English, Hindi and Gujarati. He uses well prepared PowerPoint slides for each topic and gives live demos on screen on autocad with the help of projector which I feel helps a lot in understanding better. Overall I recommend Vishal Sir for AutoCAD 2D and 3D which I learnt from him. I am looking forward to take his guidance and teaching in my future skill development for learning Solidworks.
									""', u'S
